In [511]:
cross = 15

filtro = dense_sampling['grade'] > 45

for index, row in dense_sampling[filtro].iterrows():
    
    x = row['x']
    y = row['y']
    x1 = row['x'] - cross
    x2 = row['x'] + cross
    y1 = row['y'] - cross
    y2 = row['y'] + cross
    
    row1 = df.loc[(df['x'] == x) & (df['y'] == y1)]
    row2 = df.loc[(df['x'] == x) & (df['y'] == y2)]
    row3 = df.loc[(df['x'] == x1) & (df['y'] == y)]
    row4 = df.loc[(df['x'] == x2) & (df['y'] == y)]
    
    dense_sampling = dense_sampling.append(row1, ignore_index=True)
    dense_sampling = dense_sampling.append(row2, ignore_index=True)
    dense_sampling = dense_sampling.append(row3, ignore_index=True)
    dense_sampling = dense_sampling.append(row4, ignore_index=True)
